WEBVTT

00:10.243 --> 00:12.553
It is magical, though, isn't it?

00:12.712 --> 00:15.454
That something so large can stay aloft?

00:15.615 --> 00:17.219
It's not magic, it's physics.

00:17.384 --> 00:18.419
Thrust, drag, lift.

00:19.085 --> 00:20.655
I gotta make a phone call.

00:20.820 --> 00:23.323
I thought we agreed
to set aside work for the day.

00:23.490 --> 00:25.697
You suggested it.

00:25.859 --> 00:27.736
I remained silent.

