I've got Dennis's regular columns
plus the captions.

16:22.114 --> 16:25.118
I think it's unfair that the boys here
get all the credit...

16:25.284 --> 16:27.321
...even though the girls do lots of work.

16:28.721 --> 16:31.167
Well, they write the articles.

16:31.757 --> 16:34.465
Yeah, I know, I know, but...

16:34.927 --> 16:36.929
Sometimes I think
that we could probably...

16:37.096 --> 16:39.042
...write them just as well.

16:39.198 --> 16:44.272
You know, I've seen some of your files,
and they are as good as the final copy.

16:44.436 --> 16:46.313
Why are you looking at my files?

16:47.072 --> 16:48.244
Huh?

16:48.407 --> 16:49.943
Oh, I don't--

16:50.109 --> 16:54.387
I don't remember what I saw
or why I saw it.

16:54.546 --> 16:57.049
I was just trying
to give you a compliment.

16:57.216 --> 17:00.322
I think that you are good at your job.

17:03.589 --> 17:04.795
Thanks.

17:05.023 --> 17:06.731
Any time.

17:18.737 --> 17:19.909
Will you hold this?

17:20.071 --> 17:21.813
Get my wallet out.

17:22.374 --> 17:24.718
We're heading first
to my office in Mayfair...

17:24.877 --> 17:27.380
...where you'll wait,
